<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508652>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 2. Shells of Phalium pseudobandatum, new species (A–C), P. bandatum (Perry, 1811) (D–E), and P. glaucum (Linnaeus, 1758) (F–G). A, off Sedili, Johor, Malaysia, (SH 60.3 × SW 34.4) (ZRC.MOL.3689; paratype 1); B–C, Natuna Islands, Riau, Indonesia, (SH 55.2 × SW 33.6, SH 59.3 × SW 37.3) (ZRC.MOL.3690; paratype 5 & 6). D, Townsville, Queensland, Australia (SH 83.1 × SW 52.1) (CLN); E, Olango Island, Cebu, Philippines (SH 110.9 × SW 72.2) (CNHE). F, Endau, Johor, Peninsular Malaysia (SH 101.4 × SW 67.4) (CNHE); G, Chek Jawa, Pulau Ubin, Singapore (SH 73.8 × SW 50.6) (ZRC.MOL.3687)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4508652/files/figure.png" .

